review_blob: A clean, malty Mrzen beer, a bit sweetish, but the bitterness counteracts, with a bit of citrusy acidity. I would have liked more hops in there, but its not a bad one. Very light in appearance.

beer_brewer_name: Cski Sr Manufaktra / S.C. Lixid Project S.R.L.
review_blob: Unpasteurised lager, hoppy, grassy, with a sweetish taste thats counterbalanced by a pleasant bitterness. Its a really easy to drink beer for a 6% lager.

beer_brewer_name: Bere Artizanal Sikaru / S.C. Ninkasi S.R.L.
review_blob: Very nice stout, with a great structure. Completely dry, acidic, mildly bitter, with lots of carbonation. Aromas of roast malt, caramel, coffee, and some fruit. Very easy to drink.

beer_brewer_name: Bere Artizanal Sikaru / S.C. Ninkasi S.R.L.
review_blob: Fair IPA. A bit too yeasty and cloudy. Id like it to be a bit more hoppy and/or acidic. But good nonetheless.

beer_brewer_name: Bere Artizanal Sikaru / S.C. Ninkasi S.R.L.
review_blob: A very dry & austere beer, with a sparkling wine made using the traditional method feel to it. Nice structure. I really like it, especially for the lack of bubble gum banana sweetness.
Typical weizen, but very cloudy. Kind of sweetish for my taste, but finishes with a bit of freshness. Not bad, but not my kind of beer either.
